283
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,640
I mean, Master may know of this.

284
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:30,840
The Old Madam is so cold-hearted.

285
00:15:32,119 --> 00:15:34,359
Do you see how she dotes on that Ming girl normally?

286
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,640
She got whipped twice

287
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,119
and has been kneeling for fourteen to sixteen hours!

288
00:15:38,719 --> 00:15:40,640
But the Old Madam doesn't even come to take a look?

289
00:15:42,239 --> 00:15:43,320
Yes.

290
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:44,799
You didn't sleep soundly

291
00:15:44,799 --> 00:15:46,359
at all last night.

292
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,359
But then again,

293
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,479
the Old Madam

294
00:15:50,479 --> 00:15:51,880
isn't the Master's real mother.

295
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:52,760
So naturally she's not

296
00:15:52,760 --> 00:15:54,159
the Six Miss's real grandmother either.

297
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:56,320
How much can she really dote on her?

298
00:15:56,320 --> 00:15:57,359
Just putting on the appearance of it.

299
00:15:58,239 --> 00:15:59,400
What a relief that the Old Madam

300
00:15:59,400 --> 00:16:00,719
didn't ask me for Ru'er back then,

301
00:16:01,039 --> 00:16:02,039
or my heart

302
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:03,320
will be like being fried now!

303
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,159
The Fifth Miss is the legitimate daughter of Sheng's,

304
00:16:07,159 --> 00:16:08,960
so the Old Madam wouldn't treat her the same.

305
00:16:09,239 --> 00:16:10,479
What's the difference?

306
00:16:10,479 --> 00:16:11,679
Even her own father doesn't dote on her.

307
00:16:11,760 --> 00:16:13,080
Would her father's legal mother

308
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:13,919
dote on her instead?

309
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:22,799
Greetings, Mother.

310
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:26,599
How leisurely you are.

311
00:16:27,479 --> 00:16:29,039
It's 6'o clock

312
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:30,280
and I don't dare to be lazy.

313
00:16:30,479 --> 00:16:32,320
I am on my way to the study hall to study.

314
00:16:32,799 --> 00:16:33,640
Where is Fifth Sister?

315
00:16:34,719 --> 00:16:35,960
Why don't I see her?

316
00:16:38,239 --> 00:16:39,039
Oh, I forgot!

317
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:42,320
Sister is serving the ancestors at the family shrine.

318
00:16:43,479 --> 00:16:44,359
That's good.

319
00:16:44,760 --> 00:16:46,080
It's teaching her a lesson

320
00:16:46,719 --> 00:16:47,599
lest

321
00:16:47,599 --> 00:16:49,239
when she's at the marriageable age,

322
00:16:49,559 --> 00:16:51,159
she will have a private meeting

323
00:16:51,159 --> 00:16:52,559
with a male from the outside and shame our family.

324
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,239
Shut up!

325
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,880
You little bitch!

326
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:03,159
Why can't you hold your temper like this, Mother?

327
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:05,839
You'll have lots of anger to endure

328
00:17:05,839 --> 00:17:07,839
in the future from Fifth Sister.

329
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,239
Yunzai.

330
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,079
Let's not be tardy to Scholar Zhuang's lesson.

331
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:12,680
Yes.

332
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:23,839
Speak.

333
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:26,160
Master has returned from court.

334
00:17:27,439 --> 00:17:28,479
Did he say anything?

335
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:32,560
H-He went to Linqige.

336
00:18:00,479 --> 00:18:02,040
You have been too harsh.

337
00:18:03,479 --> 00:18:04,959
Fifth Miss is so tender,

338
00:18:05,319 --> 00:18:06,599
so is Sixth Miss.

339
00:18:07,280 --> 00:18:09,079
She is the apple of Old Madam's eye.

340
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:11,599
If she kneels to be injured,

341
00:18:11,599 --> 00:18:13,640
the Old Madam won't forgive you easily.

342
00:18:19,479 --> 00:18:21,479
It's just a matter of a maiden

343
00:18:21,479 --> 00:18:23,119
stealing a look at a young man.

344
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,920
You can do that at the Dragon Boat Festival

345
00:18:25,920 --> 00:18:27,400
and you can do that at the Lantern Festival.

346
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:28,520
It's not so bad.

347
00:18:31,959 --> 00:18:33,959
Even Mencius said,

348
00:18:33,959 --> 00:18:35,800
“A child will admire his parents.

349
00:18:36,079 --> 00:18:37,479
But when he's conscious of the attractions of beauty,

350
00:18:37,479 --> 00:18:38,560
his desire is toward the young and handsome.”

351
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:39,839
Let it go.

352
00:18:40,959 --> 00:18:41,640
Let it go?

353
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,719
If you don't teach and train her well now

354
00:18:43,719 --> 00:18:44,920
to have her temper fixed,

355
00:18:44,959 --> 00:18:46,239
what will she become in the future?

356
00:18:51,920 --> 00:18:53,199
Mother is the most reasonable

357
00:18:53,199 --> 00:18:53,959
and understands discipline,

358
00:18:53,959 --> 00:18:55,119
so she will surely not blame me.

359
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,800
It's just that Minglan girl.

360
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:01,800
She's quite docile,

361
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,959
so this is a bit unfair to her.

362
00:19:05,119 --> 00:19:06,599
But that Rulan.

363
00:19:06,599 --> 00:19:08,599
Clearly she did something wrong, but she won't acknowledge it!

364
00:19:08,719 --> 00:19:09,920
She insists on framing Mo'er instead!

365
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,199
So let her keep kneeling.

366
00:19:14,839 --> 00:19:16,359
But Fifth Miss is still young.

367
00:19:17,119 --> 00:19:18,800
You should dote on her more.

368
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,439
Madam has sent someone here,

369
00:19:22,839 --> 00:19:24,680
saying she invites the Master for a chat.

370
00:19:25,920 --> 00:19:27,119
Quickly invite her in,

371
00:19:27,119 --> 00:19:28,719
and tell her he will come right over.

372
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:30,839
You make my decisions now?

373
00:19:34,719 --> 00:19:36,800
I wouldn't dare.

374
00:19:38,719 --> 00:19:40,040
Tell her to wait.

375
00:19:40,319 --> 00:19:42,119
I'm eating,

376
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:43,079
and I have matters left to attend to.

377
00:19:55,119 --> 00:19:56,199
You are just

378
00:19:58,000 --> 00:19:59,880
too generous and merciful.

379
00:20:02,119 --> 00:20:04,160
Merciful mothers ruin sons.

380
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:05,920
Your leniency is placed in wrong places!

381
00:20:07,479 --> 00:20:08,760
When it comes to treating the children well or not,

382
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:10,160
it takes great consideration.

383
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,479
If there's a merit, you reward.

384
00:20:11,479 --> 00:20:12,400
If there's a mistake, you punish.

385
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:15,079
Or else, it's no different than ruining her.

386
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:17,719
You've taught your Mo'er well.

387
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:19,479
But we need the Madam

388
00:20:19,479 --> 00:20:21,119
to teach her Ru'er well too.

389
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:26,000
What you said makes sense.

390
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,280
Master says he has matters to attend to

391
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:41,680
after eating.

392
00:20:41,839 --> 00:20:43,160
He wants you to wait,

393
00:20:43,199 --> 00:20:44,319
and he'll come when he's done.

394
00:20:45,199 --> 00:20:46,599
In that whore's room?

395
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,640
Of course he's in that whore's room.

396
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,920
Where else could he be?

397
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:03,880
Madam, don't be mad.

398
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:06,239
She's just a seductress.

399
00:21:07,319 --> 00:21:08,760
The house management rights

400
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:11,079
are still in your grasp.

401
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:13,479
Master is very angry,

402
00:21:13,479 --> 00:21:15,280
and after his anger's dissipated,

403
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:17,199
it will be easier to beg leniency

404
00:21:17,199 --> 00:21:18,839
when he comes then.

405
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:22,880
I never thought…

406
00:21:24,119 --> 00:21:26,040
This family of prestige,

407
00:21:26,040 --> 00:21:27,479
of generations of nobility,

408
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:29,040
would come to pampering of the concubine

409
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:30,439
yet slighting the main wife like this.

410
00:21:30,800 --> 00:21:32,239
If I had known,

411
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,760
Mother really shouldn't have agreed

412
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:34,680
to this marriage!

413
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,760
I wouldn't have married here!

414
00:22:03,359 --> 00:22:05,040
I already found out from the maids.

415
00:22:06,199 --> 00:22:07,640
Sixth Miss is kneeling at the shrine as punishment

416
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,439
by Minister Sheng.

417
00:22:24,319 --> 00:22:25,040
Madam.

418
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:28,239
Big Madam sent someone

419
00:22:28,239 --> 00:22:29,680
to Linqige to call the Master back.

420
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:32,719
But the Master was still angry and wouldn't go.

421
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:35,760
I saw the tonic

422
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:37,239
Madam got for Sixth Miss,

423
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:38,560
and indeed it's pretty good,

424
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,880
so Sixth Miss will suffer less.

425
00:22:42,680 --> 00:22:44,479
Big Madam put some thought into it.

426
00:22:45,880 --> 00:22:47,439
Our kitchen just said at noon

427
00:22:47,439 --> 00:22:48,599
they would send over the braised white jade fish

428
00:22:48,599 --> 00:22:51,560
Sixth Miss loves along with jasper rice.

429
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,760
What she eats isn't important right now.

430
00:22:55,079 --> 00:22:56,719
Send over a couple good pads.

431
00:22:57,359 --> 00:22:58,760
She's just being punished accompanying others,

432
00:22:58,760 --> 00:23:00,199
so she doesn't need to do this so seriously.

433
00:23:01,040 --> 00:23:03,359
That child is just so honest.

434
00:23:04,439 --> 00:23:05,839
The other one's already lying down,

435
00:23:05,839 --> 00:23:07,040
and she's still kneeling.

436
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,959
Tell her

437
00:23:08,959 --> 00:23:11,239
not to be such a hardhead.

438
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:15,040
Earlier you said just let her kneel,

439
00:23:15,319 --> 00:23:16,439
but now you care for her?

440
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:17,800
Go, go!

441
00:23:21,160 --> 00:23:22,160
Master is here.

442
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,319
It's already lunch time.

443
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:33,000
You are indeed such a nobleman with so many affairs.

444
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:39,719
So many delicious dishes.

445
00:23:46,319 --> 00:23:47,920
Salted meat and tofu with lotus seed stew?

446
00:23:49,239 --> 00:23:50,599
Great dish.

447
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,719
Add a bowl for me.

448
00:23:52,199 --> 00:23:53,160
I'll do it.

449
00:23:58,000 --> 00:24:00,119
These things are from Jinhua.

450
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:02,839
In this season, it's perfect for making it a stew.

451
00:24:06,959 --> 00:24:08,680
Here, Master.

452
00:24:16,119 --> 00:24:19,479
Master, try these dried bamboo shoots.

453
00:24:35,520 --> 00:24:36,839
Caihuan came to me earlier

454
00:24:36,839 --> 00:24:38,000
saying you wanted to speak to me.

455
00:24:41,079 --> 00:24:42,640
You must be exhausted from work

456
00:24:42,640 --> 00:24:43,680
and it's cold outside.

457
00:24:44,880 --> 00:24:46,680
Have some hot soup and food with tea.

458
00:24:46,839 --> 00:24:49,040
We can talk after you eat. There's no rush.

459
00:24:56,599 --> 00:24:58,640
If it's about Rulan,

460
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:00,520
you needn't bring it up.

461
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,800
Rulan should learn a lesson.

462
00:25:06,479 --> 00:25:09,119
What does Rulan need to learn?

463
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:14,199
You just pampered her too much,

464
00:25:14,199 --> 00:25:16,040
and she's so spoiled and ruleless.

465
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:17,479
I ask her one question

466
00:25:17,479 --> 00:25:18,680
and she retorts with ten.

467
00:25:19,119 --> 00:25:20,040
Not even half a sign

468
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,680
of a noble lady's poise.

469
00:25:23,079 --> 00:25:26,280
Master, you are her father.

470
00:25:26,599 --> 00:25:28,680
She respects and loves you.

471
00:25:29,839 --> 00:25:30,560
She was wronged

472
00:25:30,560 --> 00:25:32,119
and of course she would cry to you.

473
00:25:33,520 --> 00:25:35,319
She's a tender little maiden,

474
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:37,479
and she's been kneeling for over twenty hours!

475
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:39,640
Her knees are black and purple!

476
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,479
Master,

477
00:25:41,479 --> 00:25:43,319
spare her this time.

478
00:25:44,479 --> 00:25:45,239
I only wanted to have her

479
00:25:45,280 --> 00:25:47,239
kneel for six or eight hours at first.

480
00:25:48,040 --> 00:25:49,439
But she's scared of punishment

481
00:25:49,439 --> 00:25:50,640
and kept saying it was Mo'er's fault.

482
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,439
You see that?

483
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,280
She can lie with her eyes open.

484
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:54,319
How outrageous is that?

485
00:25:56,239 --> 00:25:57,040
Have her keep kneeling!

486
00:25:58,079 --> 00:25:58,839
If She kneels for two or three days,

487
00:25:58,839 --> 00:26:00,079
naturally she'll admit her mistake.

488
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:05,079
you say Rulan is unruly

489
00:26:05,079 --> 00:26:05,920
and wild.

490
00:26:06,719 --> 00:26:08,280
But is Hua'er mannered

491
00:26:11,719 --> 00:26:13,119
Hua'er could behave herself, of course.

492
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,079
Why are you mentioning Hua'er though?

493
00:26:15,079 --> 00:26:16,280
Who didn't envy that

494
00:26:16,280 --> 00:26:18,319
I had this great daughter Hua'er?

495
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:20,160
Back then, you described

496
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:22,119
Count Manor as so good,

497
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:23,479
and when they slighted us

498
00:26:23,479 --> 00:26:24,599
at the betrothal,

499
00:26:24,680 --> 00:26:25,920
you said to endure it.

500
00:26:26,119 --> 00:26:27,479
Since Hua'er got married there

501
00:26:27,479 --> 00:26:29,479
and she's harassed all the time by her mother-in-law

502
00:26:29,479 --> 00:26:30,359
who's biased against her!

503
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:31,439
Now she's already got

504
00:26:31,439 --> 00:26:32,920
four or five concubines crammed into her house!

505
00:26:33,079 --> 00:26:33,520
This is

506
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:35,319
the great marriage you sought for Hua'er!

507
00:26:35,439 --> 00:26:36,520
Hua'er is Hua'er,

508
00:26:36,560 --> 00:26:37,640
while Ru'er is Ru'er!

509
00:26:40,239 --> 00:26:41,119
What makes you think

510
00:26:41,119 --> 00:26:42,079
I meant no good to Hua'er?

511
00:26:46,280 --> 00:26:47,959
Yuan family is great in every way.

512
00:26:47,959 --> 00:26:49,599
It's only that Big Madam Yuan,

513
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:51,439
she prefers that eldest son

514
00:26:51,439 --> 00:26:52,839
and disregards our son-in-law!

515
00:26:53,199 --> 00:26:54,319
That's what the problem is!

516
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,119
That elder Count of the Yuan House

517
00:26:57,119 --> 00:26:58,640
is still sensible!

518
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:01,800
If you're talking about Ru'er, then stick with Ru'er.

519
00:27:02,319 --> 00:27:04,119
Don't bring other things into it.

520
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,800
Hua'er is so considerate

521
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,479
and she knows how to run a house.

522
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:11,560
She is well known for it among the Bianjing ladies.

523
00:27:12,439 --> 00:27:15,400
Changbai is so young,

524
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:16,319
but already passed the provincial exam.

525
00:27:16,959 --> 00:27:19,520
All your colleagues praise him.

526
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,479
Did those two children

527
00:27:22,479 --> 00:27:24,680
spring out of a rock then?

528
00:27:25,199 --> 00:27:27,719
They were raised by me,

529
00:27:27,719 --> 00:27:29,000
one bit of poop and urine at a time.

530
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:31,599
You did indeed go through

531
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:33,199
three letters and six courtesies,

532
00:27:33,719 --> 00:27:34,680
with the gate open

533
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:36,800
and welcomed me in as your main wife.

534
00:27:36,839 --> 00:27:40,000
Master. Master...

535
00:27:42,119 --> 00:27:44,160
Alright,

536
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:44,880
then rise.

537
00:27:48,079 --> 00:27:48,839
I dote on

538
00:27:48,839 --> 00:27:51,160
our Hua'er the most.

539
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,640
I toiled and fretted

540
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,959
to find a good marriage for her back then.

541
00:27:55,119 --> 00:27:56,839
How could I have known the Yuan's

542
00:27:56,839 --> 00:27:58,400
had that fierce and biased mother-in-law?

543
00:27:59,959 --> 00:28:02,319
When they got married,

544
00:28:02,319 --> 00:28:03,599
she put on such a good act.

545
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:05,520
We couldn't tell at all.

546
00:28:06,439 --> 00:28:07,439
Don't worry.

547
00:28:10,119 --> 00:28:12,400
Alright.

548
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,160
Sit, sit.

549
00:28:14,319 --> 00:28:15,800
Think about it.

550
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,839
Our son-in-law.

551
00:28:22,199 --> 00:28:23,160
Such a good person.

552
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,959
Patient and reasonable.

553
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,560
He's got himself a new post too.

554
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,479
A promotion!

555
00:28:28,319 --> 00:28:29,560
Later on when they move out,

556
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:30,719
Hua'er will have her share

557
00:28:30,719 --> 00:28:31,760
of wealth and honor.

558
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:33,520
Right?

559
00:28:34,319 --> 00:28:35,119
Master.

560
00:28:37,239 --> 00:28:38,160
Master.

561
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:40,119
You dote on Hua'er.

