00:40:06,479 --> 00:40:07,600
it will get either burned or trashed?

836
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,760
It's better I find one I trust to go get it,

837
00:40:09,840 --> 00:40:10,639
so I can be at ease.

838
00:40:12,040 --> 00:40:13,399
Is your home a tiger or wolf den?

839
00:40:15,159 --> 00:40:16,560
Your parents and siblings

840
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:18,399
all scheme against their own family members?

841
00:40:18,959 --> 00:40:19,840
How ridiculous.

842
00:40:21,719 --> 00:40:22,760
I come from a tiger or wolf den,

843
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:24,040
then I'm a tiger or a wolf too.

844
00:40:24,879 --> 00:40:25,320
I am no longer

845
00:40:25,399 --> 00:40:26,919
the gullible child as before.

846
00:40:27,320 --> 00:40:28,479
There is not a chance

847
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:29,840
If one wants to take advantage of me!

848
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:32,560
Then, you just be careful with all things.

849
00:40:38,199 --> 00:40:39,040
You got beaten again?

850
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:45,439
Young Lord!

851
00:40:47,399 --> 00:40:48,159
What are you doing

852
00:40:48,159 --> 00:40:49,520
with your head strained to the side?

853
00:40:49,719 --> 00:40:51,199
I'm afraid your neck can't come back around.

854
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:57,199
How is it that the three maidens

855
00:40:57,199 --> 00:40:58,280
did not show themselves today?

856
00:40:59,080 --> 00:41:01,560
Could it be that the three are all ill together?

857
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,919
Not that.

858
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:05,879
Our family invited a court nanny

859
00:41:05,879 --> 00:41:07,479
to hold lessons at home.

860
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:08,600
A Nanny from the palace?

861
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,280
Yes.

862
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,840
A few days ago,

863
00:41:11,840 --> 00:41:13,399
the girls fell down in the front hall,

864
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,600
So my father thought,

865
00:41:15,679 --> 00:41:16,919
it's better to invite someone

866
00:41:16,919 --> 00:41:17,879
to the home to teach them.

867
00:41:21,560 --> 00:41:22,760
I was present then.

868
00:41:23,239 --> 00:41:24,919
It's not such a big deal.

869
00:41:24,919 --> 00:41:26,199
You all didn't beg leniency for them?

870
00:41:26,439 --> 00:41:27,800
What's there to beg leniency for?

871
00:41:28,199 --> 00:41:29,760
It's better to have them have lessons at home

872
00:41:29,760 --> 00:41:31,080
instead of going to trouble to come to the academy hall.

873
00:41:34,040 --> 00:41:35,080
Then they won't learn books anymore?

874
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:37,399
The daughters of officials in the capital

875
00:41:37,399 --> 00:41:38,479
do not practice that.

876
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:42,120
If you get to the bottom of it,

877
00:41:42,919 --> 00:41:44,919
it's my father that rules at home.

878
00:42:00,959 --> 00:42:02,360
Eldest Master's servant

879
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,399
is following us

880
00:42:03,919 --> 00:42:04,679
With this evading and hiding,

881
00:42:04,679 --> 00:42:05,479
what is he trying to do?

882
00:42:05,719 --> 00:42:06,800
I'll dismiss him,

883
00:42:06,879 --> 00:42:07,840
so he will be out of commission

884
00:42:07,840 --> 00:42:08,800
for some eight or ten days!

885
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:11,399
He's just carrying out an order

886
00:42:11,399 --> 00:42:12,479
so you needn't do so.

887
00:42:13,479 --> 00:42:15,120
If we injure him,

888
00:42:15,120 --> 00:42:16,560
it'll come to haunt us later.

889
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,760
That house can

890
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:18,959
make a fuss out of it.

891
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:20,280
What should we do then?
